      "date": "2013-01-30 06:42:05.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 10:\n\nWe cannot use .lustre/XXX because we want to create the file as if it was in a standard directory close to some reference file. The idea is to create a file in a targeted directory, with .lustre/XXX we lose the directory reference",
